::Aerotaur/Terrataur/Aquataur::
    The missile hits Aerotaur square in the back and he careens into the 
ground.  Sparks flew from his back as he spun around to face Apewing.  "LEAVE 
ME ALONE, I'M BUSY!"  He turns around again and fires four more shots from 
each arm at Unitron.

    Terrataur looks up at Apewing and rolls her eyes.  "What you don't like 
fighting us?"  She fires two more shots at him.  Aquataur glances at 
Terrataur and smirks.  "I'm insulted, I say we kill him for that.  It 
shouldn't be too hard if he keeps ignoring us."
